---
title: Beyond Meat® with Rich Veggie Gravy with Fluffy Buttery Jasmine
description: We taken inspiration from a Hawaiian loco moco, which is a spiced beef patty topped with rich mushroom gravy and served with fluffy rice. We've turned it on its head with our plant-based version!
